
* Make appropriate changes to pg_backup.config file. (Shell script should not need to be modified)

* Set postgresql user password environment variable. Add this line to ~/.bash_profile

- export PGPASSWORD="your-psql-user-password"

* Reload

* Add everythin on the next line to crontab -e

* * * * * bash /home/eisen/olaf/olafdjango/pg_backup/pg_backup_rotated.sh -c /home/eisen/olaf/olafdjango/pg_backup/pg_backup.config